name: MyDay
0:
”Alexa, open My Day”
”Alexa, ask My Day for my fortune”
”Alexa, start My Day”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: my day
des: Start your day with a thought to meditate on or ponder. Use it as a focus or a bit of encouragement throughout the day. You can also say, "Alexa, open My Day" right before bed to get an idea that sets the tone for what you want your mind to think on with while you sleep.
priv: Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
